      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for. The exterior maintains a great shine, though you will find some light surface scratches and a few small rock chips on the hood from normal highway driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and door handles. Mechanically, it is sound and ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
