    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very sound, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience with no current mechanical issues or warning lights. The exterior is in great shape, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor rock chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. The interior is clean and has been kept smoke-free, showing only minor wear on the upholstery and floor mats. This is a dependable car that is ready for the road and would make an excellent choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
